      "text": "それ、本気で言ってます？",
      "startTime": 29.3097283444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ありませんね～。ヒントをあげましょう。もちろん\nプリンの材料は知っていますよね。常識ですよね？",
      "startTime": 37.6404527506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、牛乳、そして卵です\n酪農の大地北海道と言えば、牛乳じゃないですか",
      "startTime": 46.0404527506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
